Package tools.observer

Interface ObsInterface<T extends ObsInterface<T,​V>,​V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value used for notifying observers.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HashObservableInterface<T,​V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Button, Scheduler, SchedulerSet, SelfScheduler, ThreadScheduler
    public interface ObsInterface<T extends ObsInterface<T,​V>,​V>
    ToolObserver interface for when an object that already extends another class can still become an observer.
